<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.mcb_smart_boy.Gridix</id>
  <name>Gridix</name>
  <summary>Fast, secure database management tool with Helix/Vim keybindings</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Gridix is a fast, secure, cross-platform database management tool designed
      for keyboard enthusiasts. It features Helix/Vim-style keybindings for
      efficient navigation and editing.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Support for SQLite, PostgreSQL, and MySQL databases</li>
      <li>SSH tunnel for secure remote connections</li>
      <li>SSL/TLS encryption for MySQL</li>
      <li>AES-256-GCM encrypted password storage</li>
      <li>19 built-in color themes</li>
      <li>SQL syntax highlighting and auto-completion</li>
      <li>Data import/export (CSV, JSON, SQL)</li>
      <li>Advanced filtering with 16 operators</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

